00:29:00,800 --> 00:29:03,359
The ones who arrange the stage during scene changes?

346
00:29:03,359 --> 00:29:04,900
Something like that?

347
00:29:04,900 --> 00:29:07,200
Looking kinda cool with walkie-talkies?

348
00:29:07,950 --> 00:29:10,220
Not just arranging the stage.

349
00:29:10,220 --> 00:29:13,580
They have to be able to manage everything on the stage as well.

350
00:29:13,580 --> 00:29:16,240
What do you think? Are you interested?

351
00:29:20,860 --> 00:29:23,119
Hey! You're taking a long time to think.

