00:29:23,119 --> 00:29:25,800
I don't accept a lot of people for the backstage, you know.

353
00:29:25,800 --> 00:29:28,580
So what do you want? Are you going to do it or not?

354
00:29:30,460 --> 00:29:32,593
Yes, I'll do it.

355
00:29:32,593 --> 00:29:33,879
I'll do it.

356
00:29:33,879 --> 00:29:35,513
I will.

357
00:29:37,040 --> 00:29:38,399
You want to hold a walkie-talkie, right?

358
00:29:38,399 --> 00:29:41,139
