- Hello there.

366
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:09,479
Are you leaving, Jai?

367
00:30:09,480 --> 00:30:11,113
I'm off.

368
00:30:16,600 --> 00:30:19,699
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye, P'James.

369
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:26,240
- You...
- Hmm...

