01:00:46,480 --> 01:00:48,039
For real.

780
01:00:48,040 --> 01:00:49,799
At first, I was going to ask you to come with me.

781
01:00:49,800 --> 01:00:51,319
But it's fine, really.

782
01:00:51,320 --> 01:00:53,239
