Three...

794
01:02:50,440 --> 01:02:53,440
Why are you sitting here? Let's go dancing.

795
01:02:54,880 --> 01:02:56,519
It's okay. I don't want to.

796
01:02:56,520 --> 01:02:58,880
Hey. Come on, now.

797
01:03:34,240 --> 01:03:37,959
♫ I don't know how you are over there ♫

798
01:03:37,960 --> 01:03:41,719
♫ But all I know is that I'm over here. I can barely make it ♫

799
01:03:41,720 --> 01:03:47,639
♫ I don't need anything more than this ♫

800
01:03:47,640 --> 01:03:50,759
♫ I just want you to tuck me in ♫

801
01:03:50,760 --> 01:03:52,999
♫ Because it's late at night and I feel cold♫

802
01:03:53,000 --> 01:03:56,039
♫ The loneliness is growing every minute ♫

803
01:03:56,040 --> 01:04:02,679
♫ It'd be nice if I had you.
I wouldn't have to be lonely, but I understand ♫

804
01:04:02,680 --> 01:04:07,999
♫ I just need to see your face a bit on this lonely night ♫

805
01:04:08,000 --> 01:04:11,039
♫ Just where are you? ♫

806
01:04:11,040 --> 01:04:16,800
♫ I'm still waiting for you to come and say "Sweet dreams" ♫
